{
  "text": "In this section, for completeness, we show a derivation of the AFR [CITATION_1] illustrating explicit details for the minimization of the action functional for current fluctuations. This fluctuation relation generalizes the IFR [CITATION_2] to anisotropic systems, and was recently derived in [CITATION_3] under the hypotheses that the system satisfies: i ) reversibility and local detailed balance, ii ) time-invariance of the ODP and OCP, and iii ) space-invariance of the OCP. We take as a framework the MFT to study systems satisfying the continuity equation",
